  tasks:
  - name: Open Notebook
    description: You can view tasks, mistakes and leave the minigame with the notebook.
      Keep following the instructions to complete the tutorial.
  - name: Perform Snap Turn
    description: Flick the joystick to the left, right, or back to perform a snap
      turn. All actions can be performed with both controllers.
  - name: Teleport to White Floor
    description: Push your joystick forward to see the teleport ray. Release the
      joystick to complete the teleport. Make your way to the second bench and teleport
      onto the white teleport anchor
  - name: Click the GUI
    description: You can interact with the displays using the trigger button at the
      top of your controller. Click the X Button at the top right of this screen.
  - name: Grab the White Cube
    description: Move your hand on top of the White Cube and click the Grip Button
      on the side of the controller to grab the Cube. You can also drop objects from
      your hand using the Grip Button.
  - name: Perform Action
    description: When holding objects you can perform actions on them. Press and
      hold the trigger button that has the cube in it to turn the cube red.
  - name: Grab Distant Objects
    description: You can grab far away objects using the rays from your hand. With
      an open hand point your ray towards the Gray Cube and click the Grip Button.
  - name: Use Modifier Button
    description: Some equipment you will use have multiple actions, such as the Pipette
      Aid with dispersing. Hold a Face Button that is holding the Gray Cube to use
      the Modifier and turn the Cube Blue.
  - name: Combine Actions
    description: The pipette aid needs the Modifier button pressed to turn on dispersing
      and the Trigger button to activate it's action. Perform both actions to turn
      the Gray Cube Green.
